         <abstract id="aspace_7b195bbf9c04b40ee2c3ec51b4b90875">Programs, clippings, music, and other items relating to the Swedish soprano Jenny Lind (1820-1887), particularly regarding her American tour of 1850-1852</abstract>
      </did>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_arest">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
